<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Informix cut.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Informix cut.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Gruntal &amp; Co said it downgraded Informix Corp to neutral from &quot;outperform long-term.&quot;</p>
<p>-- Gruntal said it sees limited near-term upside in Informix's shares.</p>
<p>-- on Tuesday, Informix said it expects to post a &quot;substantial&quot; first quarter loss on weaker-than-expected sales.</p>
<p>-- Gruntal said the company will have a difficult time throughout the year &quot;making up&quot; for the expected first quarter loss.</p>
<p>-- Gruntal said cut the 1997 estimate to a loss of $0.30 a share from an earlier estimate of a profit of $1.13 a share.</p>
<p>-- Informix lost one to 8-29/32.</p>
</text>
